{"author_date": "2026-03-26T01:07:39Z", "author_login": "haakon-e", "commit_date": "2026-03-26T23:18:21Z", "committer_login": "haakon-e", "message": "fix: liquid_fraction type stability\n\nwhen calling relative_humidity without specifying\nq_liq, q_ice, they are set to Int64(0).\nThis function calls `saturation_vapor_pressure(param_set, T, q_liq, q_ice)`,\nwhich calls `\u03bb = liquid_fraction(param_set, T, q_liq, q_ice)`,\nwhich may return `q_liq / q_c`, where `q_c = q_liq + q_ice`.\nSince the numerator and denominator are integer, the result\nis Float64.\nWrap the result in FT, to ensure type stability.", "sha": "a1e2305b39045e82b1d69850715b6fde748db119"}
